## Appendix A: Technical Safeguards

Business Associate implements the following technical safeguards:

### Encryption
- Data at rest: AES-256-GCM encryption
- Data in transit: TLS 1.3+ with modern cipher suites
- Encryption key management: Industry-standard key rotation and secure storage

### Access Controls
- Role-based access control (RBAC)
- Multi-factor authentication (MFA)
- Audit logging of all PHI access
- Automatic session timeout

### Infrastructure Security
- Firewall protection
- Intrusion detection and prevention systems
- Regular security patching
- Secure backup and disaster recovery

### Monitoring
- 24/7 security monitoring
- Automated threat detection
- Regular security assessments
- Incident response procedures

